      "content": "i've tried taking a step back. i've tried working more, trying to fix things, but it's just a math problem at this point. the more i stay, the more the hole gets deeper for them. i look at the numbers and then i look at my kids and i just think... if i wasn't here, all that money would stay in our pockets. they could actually have a future instead of just surviving because of me. it's like the only way to actually help them is to just... stop being the problem.",
